# Data Access Safety

- Use parameterized SQL only.
- Avoid chatty database access; batch where possible.
- Model partition strategy explicitly for CosmosDB/DynamoDB.
- Create query-index alignment for MongoDB/CosmosDB.
- Define consistency expectations per use case.

## Quick checks

- No string-concatenated SQL
- Repository/query methods include cancellation token
- Hot partitions identified and mitigated
